  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 200°C (400°F).",
    "In a bowl, mix together the turkey, feta cheese, parsley, onion, mozzarella cheese, and Turkish Delicate Cheese.",
    "Cut the boregi pastry into squares and place a spoonful of the turkey mixture in the centre of each square.",
    "Brush the edges of the pastry with the egg and fold the pastry over to form a triangle.",
